title: Refactored the release DAO, release service and release loaders.
message:
Refactored the release DAO, release service and release loaders.

Loaders are part of the GUI, they do not belong in DB package.

Clear separations of concerns: The service contains the business logic and can access other services. It delegates calls to the DAO. The GUI does never call the DAO directly. Its calls to the services are as simple as possible, because all logic is done in the services.

Introduced application wide constants for loader IDs.
Refactored DAO's method names in the style of spring data. Removed unused query.

Introduced implicit IsHidden =! true to all find...() method in release service.
